item.title: RGMDT: Return-Gap-Minimizing Decision Tree Extraction in Non-Euclidean Metric Space
item.description: RGMDT algorithm extracts high-performing, interpretable decision trees from deep RL policies, guaranteeing near-optimal returns with size constraints, and extending to multi-agent settings.
